<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٩٩٦ - ص ر ص ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>صرصرَ يُصرصر، صرصرةً، فهو مُصرصِر وصَرْصَر<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• صَرْصَرَ الشَّخصُ:</span> صاح بصوت شديد متقطِّع.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• صرصر البازيُّ:</span> صوَّت.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>